Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:06:59.56,Extra_1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(455,0)\pos(305,113)\3c&H9E890B&\blur3}尤莉丝·爱雷克西亚·冯·里斯妃特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:06:59.56,Extra_1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(455,0)\pos(305,157)\3c&H9E890B&\blur3}华焰的魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:06:59.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决斗的规则你知道的吧
